items.description: Todo tool

items.title: Add DOMPurify for XSS protection and enhance Todo functionality
items.description:
- Integrated DOMPurify to sanitize user-generated markdown content in the TodoCard component, preventing potential XSS attacks.
- Updated the TodoBoard to utilize a computed property for managing todos by status, improving code clarity and performance.
- Refactored error handling in various async functions within the useTodoDb composable to provide better user feedback during database operations.
- Enhanced project and todo management functions to ensure consistent error handling and state updates.

items.title: Add TypeScript configuration and enhance Todo Board project persistence
items.description:
- Introduced a new `tsconfig.json` file to extend the Nuxt configuration for TypeScript support.
- Implemented functionality to persist the last used project in the Todo Board, improving user experience by restoring the last selected project on reload.
- Enhanced project selection logic to default to the first project if no previous selection exists, ensuring a smoother workflow for users.

items.title: Enhance TodoCard and TodoColumn components with content visibility features
items.description:
- Added functionality to toggle content visibility at the column level, allowing users to show or hide content for all cards within a column.
- Updated TodoCard to support markdown rendering and improved the textarea for content editing.
- Introduced computed properties for managing content visibility and rendering markdown content.
- Enhanced the TodoColumn component to include buttons for toggling content visibility, improving user interaction.
- Updated the useTodoDb composable to handle new contentCollapsed property for todos.
- Persisted column content visibility settings in local storage for a better user experience.

items.title: Add Todo Board feature and update tools index
Add new article on Canadian investment strategies for 2026
items.description:
- Introduced a comprehensive guide detailing how Canadians can effectively invest $20,000 across five tax tiers to maximize after-tax returns.
- Included an analysis of different investment vehicles, such as discount bonds and dividend ETFs, highlighting their tax implications.
- Provided a structured approach with strategies tailored for various income levels, ensuring accessibility for all Canadian investors.
- Accompanied the article with relevant images to enhance engagement and visual appeal.

items.title: Add new article on debt vs. investment strategies for Canadians in 2026
items.description:
- Introduced a comprehensive guide comparing the benefits of paying down debt versus investing extra cash, tailored for Canadian readers.
- Included detailed analysis of mortgage and HELOC interest rates, investment returns, and tax implications.
- Added practical examples and a tiered debt priority ladder to assist readers in making informed financial decisions.
- Accompanied the article with a new image to enhance visual appeal and engagement.

items.title: Update profile website configuration and enhance features
items.description:
- Added Google Sheet ID and GID for YouTube videos in `nuxt.config.ts` to facilitate video synchronization.
- Updated `package.json` and `package-lock.json` to include the `marked` package for improved markdown processing.
- Modified build and generate scripts to include a new sync script for YouTube videos.
- Enhanced header navigation by adding a link to the new YouTube Videos page.
- Expanded `summaries.json` with additional book summaries, including links to YouTube sources for better resource accessibility.

items.title: Enhance profile website with new features and updates
items.description:
- Updated `package.json` to include a new script for syncing PDF summaries and modified build and generate scripts to incorporate this functionality.
- Enhanced the header navigation by adding new tools, including a dropdown for easy access to the Canadian Tax Calculator and the new Book Summaries page.
- Introduced a new `book-summaries.vue` page to display a list of book summaries with search and filter capabilities, improving user engagement with the content.
- Added multiple PDF summaries and updated the `summaries.json` file to include detailed information about each summary, enhancing the resource library.
- Updated the `about.vue` page to include a downloadable resume link, providing users with easy access to the author's professional background.
- Created a script to automate the synchronization of PDF summaries, ensuring the data remains up-to-date and accurate.

items.title: Add Canadian Income, RRSP, and Tax Strategies article and update tax calculator UI
items.description:
- Introduced a new article detailing how income is taxed in Canada, the benefits of RRSP, and a guide to using the Canadian Tax Calculator for various income strategies.
- Updated the Canadian Tax Calculator UI to include a link to the new article, enhancing user experience and providing additional resources for understanding tax implications.
- Added a script for generating tax comparison tables for different income types, improving the article's practical application and user engagement.

items.title: Add mortgage strategies article and enhance mortgage calculator UI
items.description:
- Introduced a new article on mortgage strategies, detailing how to save money through extra payments versus investing, complete with practical examples and a comparison tool.
- Updated the mortgage calculator UI to include additional metrics such as total interest, extra principal paid, and a term summary table for improved user insights and comparisons.

items.title: Add Canadian Tax Calculator and update tools index
items.description:

- Enhanced SEO metadata for the tools section to reflect the addition of the tax calculator.

items.title: Revise mortgage calculator UI for improved clarity and comparison

items.title: implement mortgage calculator
